Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:03.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:06.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That reporter from the Weekly \NSorcerer was pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:09.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He completely ignored you, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:09.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:12.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the guild has finally calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:13.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the same way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:17.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Lucy ain't got a boyfriend as usual, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking about that again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:56.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, as happens only occasionally, \Nit is raining in Magnolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:01.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a certain out of the \Nway corner of the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:04.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a suspicious-looking magic shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:09.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drip, drip, drop...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:17.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to get him to notice you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:20.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have the perfect thing for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:24.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All Juvia wants is for him \Nto gaze in her direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drip, drip, drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:32.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not beyond the \Nability of my potions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:35.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Try using this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:41.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a potion that will get him \Nto gaze at you passionately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,60,000 jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is quite expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:46.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try and haggle, then no sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:49.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is 100% effective, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:52.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,100%... Passionate gaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drip, drip, drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:04.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This mysterious potion that \NJuvia bought at full price
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:10.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,could well bring Fairy Tail \Nto the brink of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one is yet aware of the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Request: Watch \NOut for the Guy You Like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go on a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:31.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Natsu said he wanted \Nto rest for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you go by yourself, \Nor with some other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:40.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a responsibility to \Nhim since we're on the same team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you're a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Natsu might really love you, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's the case, I think I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you two would \Nbe a good match, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:10.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsu! We'd better go \Non a job soon, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, put on some clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:17.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you use too much fire and turn \Nyour brain to charcoal, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:21.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give it a rest! You gotta take \Na day off once in a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:24.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:25.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Refresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:27.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And to refresh, you do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you two would \Nbe a good match, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:40.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,May your passionate gaze \Nonly be aimed at Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is so nerve-wracking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:50.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Juvia's hands are shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you two would make \Na good couple, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, Mira-san. Don't even joke about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous, Lucy-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:07.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...says me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:08.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting yourself in again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have something \Nimportant to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:17.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you really love my house, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:16.41,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Love
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:24.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu might really love you, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:33.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:38.06,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about something important
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:38.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Important?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:39.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's in a lousy mood today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave using the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:04.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You feelin' better?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:09.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off! Stop being all over me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:14.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. This is real bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being totally self conscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you planning on playing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, Juvia was too \Nnervous, she couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But today, Juvia has made up her mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What type of potion is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:44.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow on the contents of the flask,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and have the person you are interested \Nin swallow just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:52.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, your passionate feelings will \Nreach them, perhaps. That's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:06:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:03.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This passion burning within, growing stronger \Nand stronger as long as you are out of reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:07.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The closer Juvia gets, the \Nmore impatient she feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But today, that will all be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:16.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, Juvia and Gray-sama \Nwill be together as one, as lovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:22.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! I don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Natsu has some \Ngirl he's in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean our Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:30.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:35.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the last thing I'd \Nexpect to hear about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:40.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately he's been all "I want \Nto see her, I want to see her!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:41.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do? What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I hate him or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:51.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to love or \Ndating, well, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:55.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never gone out with a guy before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop prettifying him, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:07.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop getting wild ideas, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:09.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:17.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, I have something important \Nto talk with you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:23.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come by the Sola tree \Nin the South Gate Park tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something important to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu blushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! Where the hell do \Nyou think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:50.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Gray-sama... Your passionate gaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard... Wait, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:14.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop moving, Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, everyone is going to be \Nlooking at Juvia passionately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one needs that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally... Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Gray-sama's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:49.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...passionate gaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always flying as you \Ndamn well please in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:03.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm strong, but I can't fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're weak, but you can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, we're even!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:20.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I'm scared! Gray's acting all freaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:22.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... Where's the passionate gaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakaba, how much you make last month?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:33.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot more than you, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:38.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, especially, I won't lose to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:41.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we to each other, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rivals, of course! That's how it should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink alcohol, but don't be drowned by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:49.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You listening, alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna lose to the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:55.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is you that is my fated rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:58.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, your \Nrival is alcohol, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alcohol isn't a person. \NIt can't be your rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be drowned! I \Nwon't be drowned in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, pillar over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you always obstruct my path?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:14.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I ever wished for was to \Npass through here, unhindered,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you challenge me so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:20.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to make me your rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, being rivals with a pillar is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:28.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alcohol is one thing, but a \Npillar is right out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe if it pilloried her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just let that sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza! Let's fight like we \Nused to back in the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:41.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are my lifelong rival, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:48.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to fly farther \Nthan you, without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I will fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Against you... Against my rival...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not lose, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go, Natsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:10.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that it takes some time \Nbefore the potion takes effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:14.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think an explanation is in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:22.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something I mixed up with a \Nbunch of forbidden magical ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what effect it might have?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:28.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why would I do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:31.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I needed some cash to make a getaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What will become of Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do? What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come by the Sola tree \Nin the South Gate Park tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something important to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do? What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This has got to be a love \Nconfession! Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:04.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to turn him down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're on the same team...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect chance to wear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, this will work great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:19.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.  This is all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! What the heck are you thinking, Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, what'll I do? What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Giant Crab, I open thee! Cancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me look cute, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish-ebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:37.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, I ended up doing it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:56.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have 30 babies together, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:57.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that's not how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:10.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why were they Happys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a drinking contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My rival is alcohol itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three against three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:29.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go thinking that just because we're \Nequal in number, we're equal in ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:34.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk about teams of three \Nin Fairy Tail, it always means us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:35.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no real Man here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a rival for me, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am saddened! I am violently saddened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:46.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so he thinks he has no rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does he get that self-confidence from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:50.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You finished adding it up, rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:54.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! And faster than you, rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a little dull in the tooth, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the count of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:02.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The amount of money I made last month is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,150,000 jewel all in all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:11.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll do battle with \Nthe month before last!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We Raijin Tribe versus you Shadow Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:19.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll decide just who is the best \Nthree-person team in Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be surprised when you see our skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're having a posing competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is a Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-chan, that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you lookin' good today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:46.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go fallin' in the \Nriver before your date!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:49.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Date?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:57.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. At least I look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this is all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:01.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All wrong! All wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:14.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not gonna work! We're co-workers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:17.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be together with Natsu for...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:21.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together forever, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:23.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Together forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Wheel Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We just rebuilt the place! \NDon't go destroying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:39.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is constantly standing up in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:42.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It especially makes me angry when I wish \Nto go further inside without delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:46.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to go further \Nin without going around it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is this pillar that is \Nalways standing in my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,in other words, my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you just have to \Ngo around it a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:55.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you like to take things \Nstraight on, but sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:59.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza tends not to look where she's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:03.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:04.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your rival is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:08.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm facing down my lifelong rival right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it's just a pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:15.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Satan Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip! Purgatory Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, just stop, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:27.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wildcat... Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:31.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's a real Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:34.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:37.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guild's gonna be destroyed again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:44.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, it's impossible, I tell you! Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to surpass you, my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is so vexed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:51.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More potion...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:56.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, my rival! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:07.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even more fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:09.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's all like Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:12.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:22.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:23.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:32.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sola tree in South Gate Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:39.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together... Stay calm, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:42.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:46.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do? What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:52.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pushover when it comes to pushy people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late! Out with that \Nmaid of yours already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was her name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know... Right, Virgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground's really hard here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to dig it up \Nwithout that Spirit maid of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the important thing \Nyou wanted to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear there's a treasure buried here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:24.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be an album of embarrassing \Npictures of everyone in Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:27.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps hid it here a long time ago, I heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this gonna be fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:34.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And...the girl you fell \Nin love with recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:38.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were saying "I want to \Nsee her, I want to see her."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:43.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I care one way \Nor the other, but it was Virgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping she'd dig the hole for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:51.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hole?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:05.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am such a total fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And, just like the previous episode, \NLucy is disappointed in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:17.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:29.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, hang in there! It's \Nmorning already, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia! You came to save him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To make you go through all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:44.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason the potion\Ndidn't work correctly is surely
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:47.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,because Juvia's feelings\Nfor you weren't strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:00.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia? What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe... Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She lllikes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:07.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I was cold for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:09.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop gettin' me all soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:11.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Juvia is shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:17.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't enough, it just isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:24.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is breakin' out the potion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:32.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:35.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Horizon over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:38.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:41.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:42.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:45.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess some people weren't meant to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:49.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And, just like Lucy, Juvia \Nis disappointed in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:53.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A few days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:21:58.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:01.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking...
